program 1: this is just a basic pointer warm up excerise, just reassigns varibles, and gets user imput
program 2: populates two arrays, one with integers, and one with letters, prints contents of even indices
program 3: creates 3 arrays, populates array 2/3 with integers from array 1, sums and aberages the values in array 2 and 3

To compile the programs run: 
make

to run problem 1: ./P1A1
to run problem 2: ./P2A1
to run problem 3: ./P3A1

the typescript shows the making and execution of all three files, and some sample input for P1A1
